OL,3,CManchester City's Rodri wins Ballon
OL,4,Cd'Or
OL,6,FManchester City midfielder Rodri has
OL,7,Fbeen crowned this year's best
OL,8,Ffootballer at the men's Ballon d'Or in
OL,9,FParis.
OL,11,FRodri beat the Real Madrid trio of
OL,12,FVinicius Junior, Dani Carvajal and
OL,13,FJude Bellingham to the top honour,
OL,14,Fcausing the Spanish giants to claim
OL,15,F"the Ballon d'Or does not respect Real
OL,16,FMadrid" and refuse to attend the
OL,17,Fceremony.
