OL,3,CManchester City's Rodri wins Ballon
OL,4,Cd'Or
OL,6,FRecognition came for the defensive
OL,7,Fmidfielder at the end of a year in
OL,8,Fwhich he helped Spain to glory at the
OL,9,FEuros while also lifting the Premier
OL,10,FLeague trophy for a fourth consecutive
OL,11,Fseason with City.
OL,13,FThe 28-year-old, who is the first ever
OL,14,FManchester City player to be presented
OL,15,Fwith the accolade, was helped on to
OL,16,Fthe stage on crutches after his season-
OL,17,Fending knee ligament injury.
