OL,3,CManchester City's Rodri wins Ballon
OL,4,Cd'Or
OL,6,FSpeaking in Spanish, Rodri said: "I
OL,7,Fhave so many things to thank people
OL,8,Ffor. First of all to France Football
OL,9,Fand to UEFA for giving me this award.
OL,11,F"I would like to thank those who voted
OL,12,Ffor me and put their trust in me.
OL,13,FToday is a very special day for me and
OL,14,Ffor my family, my country.
OL,16,F"I would like to thank the most
OL,17,Fimportant person in the world for me,
OL,18,Fmy girlfriend Laura. Today is our
OL,19,Fanniversary and without her things
OL,20,Fwouldn't have been the same. Thank you.
