OL,6,F"Also my family, of course. The values
OL,7,Fthey have taught me and all they
OL,8,Frepresent in me, for having taught me
OL,9,Fthe right steps to take and for
OL,10,Fhelping be become the man I am...
OL,12,F"I don't want to forget my team-mates,
OL,13,FI understand it is a group game.
OL,14,FManchester City is so special, I know
OL,15,FI wouldn't make this without you. For
OL,16,Fme it is the best club in the world,
OL,17,Fand thanks to them things happen much
OL,18,Feasier.
