OL,6,F"The national team and Luis (de la
OL,7,FFuente, coach), for trusting me for so
OL,8,Flong, I have to mention my team-mates
OL,9,Fwith whom we won the Euros. This is
OL,10,Fnot just for me but for Spanish
OL,11,Ffootball."
OL,13,FReal Madrid had somewhat signalled
OL,14,FRodri's success before the ceremony
OL,15,Fbegan as their delegation cancelled
OL,16,Ftheir trip to the French capital.
