OL,6,FIn a statement reported by Spanish
OL,7,Fnewspaper AS, the club said: "If the
OL,8,Faward criteria doesn't give it to
OL,9,FVinicius as the winner, then those
OL,10,Fsame criteria should point to (Dani)
OL,11,FCarvajal as the winner.
OL,13,F"As this was not the case, it is clear
OL,14,Fthat Ballon d'Or does not respect Real
OL,15,FMadrid. Real Madrid does not go where
OL,16,Fit is not respected."
