OL,6,FMadrid finished the night with two
OL,7,Fawards and a share of a third, and
OL,8,Fwith four players in the top six in
OL,9,Fthe final ranking for the men's Ballon
OL,10,Fd'Or ` Vinicius, Bellingham, Carvajal
OL,11,Fand Kylian Mbappe, who finished sixth
OL,12,Fin the voting, one place behind
OL,13,FRodri's team-mate Erling Haaland.
